Akwai damuwa tsakanin wasu 'yan majalisa game da shawarar canza taken su daga AMe zuwa MWPe (don Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan ya faru ne saboda shirin canja sunan taron zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
'Yan siyasa a duk faɗin duniya suna tsoron cewa hakan zai iya jawo ba'a.
Wani ɗan jam'iyyar Labour ya ce ƙungiyarsa ta damu domin "ta yi magana da Twp da Pwp".
