A bayyane yake cewa 'yan majalisar suna gabatar da wasu hanyoyin, amma gwagwarmayar samun jituwa na iya zama ciwon kai ga shugaban kasa, Elin Jones, wanda zai gabatar da kudurinsa a cikin makonni.
