Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya kaddamar da taron zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka ajiye kuri'ar tabbatarwa a yanzu don zaɓensa na cike gibin kotun koli, Trump na shirin gina goyon baya ga zaɓen tazara mai zuwa saboda Republican na cikin haɗarin rasa iko a kan Majalisa lokacin da aka jefa kuri'a a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia ya faru a daren yau, kuma yaya za a duba taron a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, don 7pm ET a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa.
Trump zai yi magana a kan shari'ar da aka yi a wannan makon don wanda aka nada a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya damu game da zargin lalata da aka yi masa da kuma an yi masa alkawarin cewa zai iya tabbatar da hakan har sai da mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma, babban abin da ake nufi da wannan taro mai yawa shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da suke fuskantar babban zaben a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce, waɗannan tarurrukan biyar na mako mai zuwa suna nufin "ziyarar masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da faɗaɗa rinjayen da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma Majalisar Wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a kan majalisa tana da matukar muhimmanci ga tsarinsa na siyasa da shugaban kasa zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama da zai yiwu idan muka kai lokacin yakin neman zabe", wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya ki a ambaci sunansa, ya shaida wa Reuters.
A yau da dare, ana shirya taron a filin wasa na Westbanco a Wheeling, ana iya jawo masu goyon baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ana iya samun labarai a Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne zai zama karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe ta da sama da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Jam'iyyar Republican ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya rage bisa ga tsarin zabe.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya ba shi ƙarin ƙarfi a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
