Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta yi amfani da makamai ba
A ranar Asabar, ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ci gaba da saka takunkumi yana ƙara ƙaruwa ga rashin amincewarsu da Amurka kuma ba shakka ba za ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliya ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya gaya wa taron shekara - shekara na hukumar duniya cewa a cikin shekarar da ta shige, Koriya ta Arewa ta ɗauki "hanyoyin alheri masu muhimmanci", kamar su dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na makami mai linzami, ta rushe filin gwajin makaman nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin da ba za ta ƙara yin amfani da makamai da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Amma ba mu ga irin wannan martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, babu amincewa da tsaronmu na kasa, kuma a irin wannan yanayin, ba za mu fara yin amfani da makamai ba".
Yayin da Ri ya maimaita sanannun korafin da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi game da yadda Washington ke tsayayya da "ƙaddamarwa" ta kawar da makaman nukiliya da za ta ba da lada ga Koriya ta Arewa idan ta yi wani mataki na ci gaba, kalmominsa sun zama masu ma'ana domin ba ta ƙaryata game da kawar da makaman nukiliya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne game da wata sanarwa da Kim Jong-un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko da aka yi tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don "halaka makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbacin tsaro ga Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa tana son a kawo ƙarshen yaƙin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amirka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta daina yin amfani da makaman nukiliya.
Washington ta kuma ƙi roƙon da ake yi ta sassauta tsauraran takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka yi wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta nace da 'kashe makaman nukiliya da farko' kuma ta ƙara matsa lamba ta hanyar tsaurara matakin takunkumi don cimma burinsu ta hanyar da ta dace, har ma da yin adawa da 'bayyana ƙarshen yaƙi,'" in ji Ri.
"Hikima cewa takunkumi za su iya sa mu durƙusa a kan gwiwoyinmu mafarki ne na mutanen da ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da saka hannu a wannan matakin zai ƙara ɓata mana amana".
Ri bai yi sharhi ba game da shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump da shugaban Amurka ya yi magana da shi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka, ya mai da hankali ga tarurruka uku da aka yi a cikin watanni biyar da suka shige tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in, ya daɗa: "Idan da ita ce ta yi magana game da batun halakar makaman nukiliya, amma ba Amurka ba, da a ce an yi ta halakar makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya ta Kudu ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na bara, lokacin da ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba za a iya kauce wa roket din Koriya ta Arewa da za a kai wa Amurka hari ba bayan "Mista Bad President" Trump ya kira Kim "mai harbi" a kan wani shiri na kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda ya yi barazanar "dakatar da Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya" a bara, ya yaba wa Kim sosai don ƙarfin hali da ya nuna don yin matakan kawar da makamai, amma ya ce akwai aiki mai yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da tsai da hukuncin har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da wani lokaci don yin hakan, yana cewa "Ba kome ko yana daukan shekaru biyu, shekaru uku, ko watanni biyar".
Kasashen Sin da Rasha sun yi imanin cewa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci Pyongyang ta biya wa 'yan ta'adda da suka yi.
Amma, a ranar Alhamis, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa: "Domin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ci gaba da bin doka, dole ne a ci gaba da bin doka har sai mun kammala kammala kawar da makaman nukiliya".
Tun shekara ta 2006, Majalisar Tsaro ta tsaurara takunkumi a kan Koriya ta Arewa a matsayin yarjejeniya don ta rage kudade don shirin nukiliya da kuma makaman nukiliya na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a wajen taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, kuma ya ce zai sake ziyarci Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ba ya tafiya sosai a ziyararsa ta ƙarshe.
Ya bar birnin Pyongyang a watan Yuli, yana cewa an samu ci gaba, amma bayan sa'o'i kaɗan, Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi da "da'awar da ta dace".
A wani taron da ta yi da Moon, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe wani makami mai linzami da kuma makami mai linzami idan Amurka ta ɗauki "matakin da ya dace".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake son gani sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma matakan daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna bin wani darasi game da isasshen hutawa
Wani sabon shiri a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya sa dukan dalibansa na digiri na biyu su samu karin barci a ƙoƙarin su magance al'adun macho na nazari ta hanyar yin "saƙon taro" da ke da kafe.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗaliban jami'o'i masu daraja a duniya ba su san ainihin yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Czeisler, wani farfesa a fannin maganin barci a Harvard Medical School kuma gwani a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya tsara wannan hanya, wadda ya yi imanin cewa ita ce ta farko a Amirka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi ya fara wannan darasi bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
"A ƙarshen wannan, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, 'Me ya sa suke gaya mini haka yanzu, a shekaruna na ƙarshe?'
Ta ce ba wanda ya gaya mata muhimmancin barci - abin da ya ba ni mamaki,' in ji shi ga The Telegraph.
Wannan darasin, wanda aka fara yi a wannan shekara, ya bayyana wa ɗalibai ainihin yadda yin barci da kyau yake taimaka wa ɗalibai su yi nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni, da kuma yadda yake inganta lafiyarsu gaba ɗaya.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar mutum a Harvard Medical School kuma darektan kula da lafiyar jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar soma wannan aikin bayan an gano cewa ɗalibai sun yi rashin barci sosai a lokacin makon.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashe, akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai suke danna kofi, labule, takalma, da littattafai don a gaya musu yadda maganin kafeyin da haske suke shafar su da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin tsarin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar da ke ɗauke da gumaka masu ma'amala, ta ƙarfafa mahalarta su yi tunani a kan ayyukan yau da kullum.
"Mun san cewa ba zai canja halin ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da hakkin su sani - kamar yadda kai ma kana da hakkin ka san sakamakon da shan sigari zai kawo a kan lafiyarka,' in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce har ila akwai al'adar yin alfahari da "koyon dare", kuma ya ƙara da cewa fasahar zamani da kuma matsin lamba a kan ɗalibai ya sa rashin barci ya zama matsala mai yawa.
Ya ce, don a tabbata cewa kana samun isasshen barci mai kyau, ɗalibin ya kamata ya yi amfani da shi a matsayin "makamin asiri" don ya guji damuwa, gajiya, da kuma damuwa - har ma don ya guji yin nauyi, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta kasance cikin yanayin yunwa, wanda ke sa ka ji yunwa a kowane lokaci.
Raymond So, ɗan shekara 19 a California, mai nazarin kimiya da kuma ilimin halittu, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler ya tsara wannan darasin bayan ya halarci ɗayan darussansa a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard a bara.
Ya ce wannan darasin ya buɗe idanunsa kuma ya motsa shi ya yi ƙoƙari ya yi nazarin dukan makarantar.
Ya yi fatan cewa mataki na gaba shi ne a gaya wa dukan ɗaliban digiri na biyu su kammala irin wannan shirin kafin su shiga makarantar da mutane suke fafatawa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da yin amfani da ƙararrawa don lokacin barci da lokacin farkawa, da kuma sanin haɗarin "hasken blue" da aka nuna ta hanyar allon lantarki da hasken LED, wanda zai iya ɓata saurin wasan kwaikwayo kuma ya sa ka yi fama da tuntuɓar tumaki.
Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Manufar Menga ta ci Gerrard 'yan adam
Yan Rangers sun sake fuskantar wata damuwa a lokacin da Dolly Menga ta kai wa Steven Gerrard rashin nasara 1-0 a baya.
Tawagar Ibrox ta yi niyyar samun nasarar da ta fara samu a matsayin baƙo tun daga nasarar 4-1 da ta yi a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma Gary Holt ya ba Gerrard na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin mai gudanarwa don haka tawagarsa ta kasance maki takwas a baya na Hearts, wanda ya ci gaba da samun nasara a Ladbrokes Premiership.
Menga ya buga a minti bakwai kafin lokacin hutu, kuma ba a ganin cewa Rangers za su yi wasa ba tare da samun ƙarin wahayi ba.
Yayin da Rangers suka koma matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa matsayi na uku, yana daurewa bayan Hibernian a raga.
Kuma za a iya samun ƙarin matsala ga Rangers bayan da aka yi wa alkalin kan iyaka Calum Spence magani don raunin kai bayan da aka jefa wani abu a gefe.
Gerrand ya yi canje-canje takwas a cikin tawagar da ta wuce Ayr bayan wasan karshe na kofin Betfred.
Holt, a gefe guda, yana amfani da wannan Livi-11 wanda ya dauki wani maki daga Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai kasance a cikin sahunsa da yadda ƙungiyarsa mai horo ta yi wa abokan hamayyarsu rauni a kowane juyi.
Wataƙila Rangers sun mallaki kwallon, amma Livingston ya yi fiye da haka sa'ad da suke da ball.
Da farko dai, ya kamata su ci maki bayan minti biyu da suka wuce, lokacin da aka tura Scott Pittman a raga na Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan ya yi amfani da babbar damarsa.
An samu wani babban dan wasan da Keaghan Jacobs ya sa shi a baya, Captain Craig Halkett, amma abokin aikinsa na tsaron Alan Lithgow ya rasa hanya ta ci gaba da tseren.
'Yan wasan sun ci gaba da yin nasara, amma a ƙarshen wasan, sun ga cewa akwai bege fiye da tabbaci.
Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa ya samu burin kisa a lokacin da ya yi faɗa da Steven Lawless, amma alkalin kotun Steven Thomson ya ƙi roƙon ɗan Colombia.
Yan Rangers sun yi nasarar samun harbi biyu kawai a cikin rabin rabin rabin amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Ibrox Liam Kelly ya damu da mummunan harbin da Lassana Coulibaly ya yi da kuma Ovie Ejaria ya yi.
Ko da yake Livi ya yi nasara a minti na 34, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan, ko da yake sun yi aiki tuƙuru don hakan.
A wannan lokacin, 'yan tsaron sun kasa yin amfani da wasu kayan Jacobs masu zurfi.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya aika da kwallon ga Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai sanyi kuma ya aika da shi ga Menga don kawai sake zagayowar.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu lokacin da ya musanya Coulibaly don Ryan Kent kuma musayar ta yi tasiri kusan nan take lokacin da fage ya tura Morelos amma ya kori Kelly mai ban sha'awa daga layinsa zuwa ga block.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da tilasta wa baƙi su yi wasa daidai da irin wasan da suke so, da Lithgow da Halkett suka yi wasa da dogon ball bayan dogon ball.
Ƙungiyar Holt za ta iya ƙara musu jagora a matakai na ƙarshe, amma McGregor ya tashi da kyau don ya juya Jacobs kafin Lithgow ta iya shiga daga kusurwa.
Glenn Middleton, wanda ya maye gurbin Rangers, ya yi wani laifi a lokacin da ya yi rikici da Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake yin watsi da shi.
