Kudaden da kasar Sin ta biya a farkon yakin cinikayya na nufin kashe masu fitar da kaya a jihohi kamar Iowa da suka goyi bayan Jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, masana na kasar Sin da Amurka sun ce.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa na dogon lokaci, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kuma kamfanoni.
