Gidan White House ya ce za a iya sake jinkirta taron Trump da Rosenstein
Taron Donald Trump mai haɗari tare da mataimakin babban lauya Rod Rosenstein na iya "kasancewa da sati guda" yayin da ake ci gaba da gwagwarmaya game da dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein ya lura da aikin mai ba da shawara na musamman na shari'a Robert Mueller, wanda ke bincika tsoma baki na Rasha a zaben, alaƙa tsakanin magoya bayan Trump da Rasha da yiwuwar mamaye doka ta shugaban kasa.
Ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauya ko a'a, kuma hakan zai yi barazanar 'yancin kai na Mueller, ya shafe watanni yana tayar da jita-jita a Washington.
A farkon wannan watan, New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna yiwuwar saka mai rikodin sauti don yin rikodin tattaunawa da Trump, da kuma yiwuwar cire shugaban ta hanyar Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta rahoton.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta shige, ya je fadar White House, a tsakiyar rahotanni cewa yana kan hanyar yin murna.
A maimakon haka, an sanar da cewa za a yi taro da Trump, wanda a lokacin yake Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York, a ranar Alhamis.
Trump ya ce zai "zaɓa kada" ya yi wa Rosenstein ba'a, amma sai aka soke taron don kauce wa rikici da kotun Majalisar Dattawa ta yi a lokacin da Kavanaugh da kuma ɗaya daga cikin matan da suka zarge shi da lalata, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, suka shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya gudanar da bincike na mako guda na FBI kan zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh kuma ya jinkirta kammala zaben Majalisar Dattijai.
Sakataren yada labarai na Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a Fox News a ranar Lahadi.
Sa'ad da aka tambaye ta game da taron Rosenstein, ta ce: "Ba a riga an ba da kwanan wata ba, za a iya yin hakan a wannan makon, ina ganin an sake jinkirta shi da mako guda tare da dukan sauran al'amuran da suka shafi kotun koli.
Amma za mu ga kuma ina son in riƙa sanar da manema labarai".
Wasu 'yan jarida za su ƙi wannan bayanin: Sanders bai yi jawabi a fadar White House ba tun ranar 10 ga Satumba.
Mai watsa shiri Chris Wallace ya tambaye me ya sa.
Sanders ta ce rashin samun zaman labarai ba don rashin fahimta ba ne ga 'yan jaridar TV da suke "sha'awar tasiri", ko da yake ta ce: "Ba zan yi jayayya da cewa suna da tasiri ba".
Ta yi nuni da cewa za a kara samun lamba kai tsaye tsakanin Trump da manema labarai.
"Shugaban kasa ya yi tambayoyi da tambayoyi fiye da kowane shugaban kasa a gabansa", in ji ta, kuma ba tare da ta ambata shaidar ba, ta kara da cewa, "Mun duba lambobin".
Sanders ya ce za a ci gaba da yin taro, amma "idan 'yan jarida suna da damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, to, ya fi kyau su yi magana da ni.
Muna yin ƙoƙari sosai kuma kun ga muna yin hakan sosai a cikin 'yan makonnin da suka gabata kuma zai maye gurbin zaman tattaunawa da shugaban Amurka".
Trump yana amsa tambayoyi a kai a kai lokacin da ya bar Fadar White House ko kuma ya halarci tarurruka na bude ido ko kuma sanarwar manema labarai tare da masu daraja da ke ziyartar.
Ba a yawan samun sanarwar da aka yi wa manema labarai.
