A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa, in ji Hukumar Kashe Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya kai wa yankin yammacin Donggala hari kuma ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane tara.
